","parent":"152","text":"Evitar agua caliente y frotamiento vigoroso","guid":"wUgfFyYq_xUvDxlQQgwTiQ","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Hidratación con emolientes 2 veces/día","guid":"HR8bEpKB7w5IRqgBPOJ4pQ","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Ácidos grasos hiperoxigenados (AGHO) → Mepentol","guid":"5KI8bc9ZA7Y0NhyrM6FQPQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"NO masajear prominencias óseas (puede dañar tejido)","guid":"WxyX4-p39QiRuxHRSXsABw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"152","text":"Protectores cutáneos → Cavilon (película barrera sin alcohol)","guid":"0AEbAL0wWZhqnBvOpqrb4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"141","text":"Estrategia 3 → Manejo de Humedad","guid":"TtBR-wbHckqPXQpwbXl5_w","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"Absorbentes apropiados","guid":"MoEMtv8yctNcxifQTn6a1w","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"Cambio precoz tras incontinencia","guid":"21a_lP6Np-1vE9c8XfkBBQ","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"Barrera cutánea → óxido de zinc, Cavilon, Sudocrem","guid":"NtViVWVAYCC0TB4RdNaT9A","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"160","text":"Tratamiento de diarrea / poliuria","guid":"q8h21rzZrkdiCIvO0s0CBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"141","text":"Estrategia 4 → Nutrición","guid":"2pk8GTgN4dW7d-ghrmDWWg","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"Screening MNA / NRS-2002","guid":"MNGQPh6_RqKS16WukHOCJg","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"Aporte calórico 30-35 kcal/kg/día","guid":"LbUxWZQBVY3fVIZElJHuIQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"Proteínas 1.25-1.5 g/kg/día","guid":"1QmUj5W_qMZ0RB9g1CIDvg","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"Hidratación 30 ml/kg/día","guid":"GaSzWQ3NIROZJkuEnDdoEQ","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"165","text":"Suplementación con ARGININA + zinc + vit C en riesgo alto","guid":"Honzv_WJpn9ANlOf08laHw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"Suplementos orales específicos para