V4ezSzj_Cg5THN-Mg","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"Absorbe olor","guid":"w0y5-jCPoPnQwXrDflxhhA","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"Con o sin plata","guid":"cHybZBbZQU6FbO2a9ALOxw","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"248","text":"Indicación → heridas malolientes, neoplásicas","guid":"edxFoZhLSDUYHKJripVWGQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"248","text":"Marca Chile → Actisorb Plus 25 (Systagenix/3M), Carboflex (ConvaTec)","guid":"o3w57ayRjwfDoEAtsc6HeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"198","text":"Moduladores de metaloproteinasas","guid":"UOxta8QrctjrB5W8zL6aSg","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"Colágeno oxidado + celulosa","guid":"6xS0Fer_KDi4GZjtggp45g","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"Reducen MMPs elevadas en heridas crónicas","guid":"4W_VZYYXWRJ4_ZDm2Q71Og","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"253","text":"Heridas estancadas sin progresión","guid":"xwk2k5gpSfr25D3IBCEPCg","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"253","text":"Marcas Chile → Promogran / Promogran Prisma (Systagenix/3M), UrgoStart (Urgo → TLC-NOSF)","guid":"-7PpSknYfCWC9A4RK4Cq0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"198","text":"Películas transparentes de poliuretano","guid":"qCqEY9m5AxV2VcbK-cOq6g","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"Semipermeables","guid":"4p0FiOdTZfiGVPrFjf-NvA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"Indicación → etapa 1, fijación catéteres, protección zonas riesgo","guid":"u39f6kTZsTf3jvKdcdj9iw","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"258","text":"NO absorben","guid":"CeuqTmSpcNW6WmUd9CGxhQ","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"258","text":"Marcas Chile → Tegaderm Film (3M/Solventum), Opsite (Smith&Nephew), Hydrofilm (Hartmann)","guid":"XU9tH36_f0-GXvffy86T4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"198","text":"Protectores cutáneos y barreras","guid":"x5fUydDmNVK37OfF0qEnEg","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"Películas barrera sin alcohol → Cavilon No Sting (3M/Solventum), Silesse (ConvaTec), Brava (Coloplast)","guid":"QGGbqdVeiumInYEHMQpKRA","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"Cremas barrera → Cavilon Durable, Sudocrem","guid":"H60ofe_AcHx1ddA9OCI9Kg","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"Indicación → piel perilesional, incontinencia","guid":"aKyhxyMnA01fAU370mvJhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"198","text":"Matriz atraumática (contacto)","guid":"x377AkRpvTzc0v_deZxApQ","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"Silicona o lípido-coloide → no adherente","guid":"aUfyKXGf7ECZM4446dy9zA","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"Protege lecho, permite paso exudado","guid":"jlPnT7gP6Jy15ix-H9fw7A","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"267","text":"Marcas Chile → Mepitel / Mepitel One (Mölnlycke), Urgotul / Urgotul Ag (Urgo), Atrauman (Hartmann), Adaptic (Systagenix)","guid":"d6YHWhPpTzmSCM2n1g-VIQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"271","parent":"181","text":"Terapia de Presión Negativa (TPN / VAC)","guid":"mtzt-Ug8fzKflRwd1mtuIg","children":[{"id":"272","parent":"271","text":"Indicación → LPP etapa 3-4 con exudado alto, tras desbridamiento","guid":"GeXtwEiTRoZzjS0cUokQRQ","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"271","text":"Presión típica 125 mmHg continua o intermitente","guid":"jMp30FCD_mkllw0Upe20Ow","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"271","text":"Presión 150-200 mmHg si exudado abundante","guid":"0dA0lJQTd_4wZCIoYxMIuQ","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"271","text":"Duración hasta lecho limpio (~20 días máx)","guid":"-uLJMOW2HeCiAQvS7sNwDQ","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"271","text":"Contraindicada → necrosis no desbridada, osteomielitis no tratada, neoplasia, fístula órgano","guid":"otz6xAfk1rwJnBOoaOKwDw","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"271","text":"Marcas Chile → V.A.C. Therapy (KCI/3M), PICO (Smith&Nephew → desechable)","guid":"4PK2Z3002_ZjGI95mHB_nw","children":[]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"181","text":"Desbridamiento","guid":"TxUO_ut3lvGoRYvbCR3vIA","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"Cortante → gold standard, rápido, en box procedimientos","guid":"QsxYe7hU766mBZLvxawtqA","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"278","text":"Enzimático → colagenasa (Iruxol)","guid":"3PrpzlNEnf1y5j6szaGMnw","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"278","text":"Autolítico → hidrogel + apósito oclusivo","guid":"lTXkxJ9-mzVLtdamv9DgNw","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"278","text":"Mecánico → wet-to-dry, duchoterapia agresiva","guid":"o74ddE4NFdv6VfsTTnunAg","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"278","text":"Osmótico → apósitos hipertónicos (Mesalt)","guid":"kCInY035s5ebDYwP6cYE_g","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"278","text":"Biológico → larvas (no disponible masivamente Chile)","guid":"vjsByLyaNBz8Kd3moBWOyA","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"278","text":"NO desbridar talón con escara seca ESTABLE sin signos inflamación (AGS)","guid":"2FnfPNQT16dI7kfuOzpSeA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"286","parent":"0","text":"Nutrición y Cicatrización","guid":"sJxvvmNbsPJpZ_CSrQ-Mbg","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"Evaluación → MNA, albúmina, prealbúmina, linfocitos, peso","guid":"4tnPECVJvm5ubADMvAe3yA","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"286","text":"Calorías 30-35 kcal/kg/día","guid":"fqQY2m9jGP188sFhMi-qdA","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"286","text":"Proteína 1.25-1.5 g/kg/día (hasta 2 g/kg en LPP 3-4)","guid":"dlG15fmKJbLYizHdGDaqsg","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"286","text":"Micronutrientes → zinc, vit C, vit A, arginina, HMB","guid":"lROwPKtvAjfgs-Biu_Sg_A","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"286","text":"Suplementos específicos → Cubitan (Nutricia), Juven (Abbott), Ensure Plus (Abbott)","guid":"7qv8RvfMkz94mmzsXqz6NA","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"286","text":"Hidratación 30 ml/kg/día","guid":"IhRv9r7kB3Wd9yFKcNk8VA","children":[]}]},{"id":"293","parent":"0","text":"Manejo del Dolor","guid":"klT9sa53rpcAhQbdPuJEkg","children":[{"id":"294","parent":"293","text":"Evaluación → EVA, ESCID en no comunicante","guid":"Gce28uv9WeLrU2thVBevaw","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"293","text":"Analgesia basal + previa a curación","guid":"rG-rZRXMoQTsWsQgDaMkYg","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"293","text":"Considerar opioide de acción corta 30 min pre-curación","guid":"ANtspIEQVSsbIkcnq5dSug","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"293","text":"Apósitos atraumáticos (silicona) → reducen dolor al recambio","guid":"Vy670T7926NLKPs5apoeww","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"293","text":"Lidocaína tópica en gel 2% off-label (evidencia limitada)","guid":"RLl79KBrV3pVZGL-RslaHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"299","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones Geriátricas","guid":"scf7zYPLgjodeQ-mnL5Iiw","children":[{"id":"300","parent":"299","text":"Polifarmacia → revisar corticoides sistémicos, AINEs, vasoactivos (STOPP/START)","guid":"MoMovmmf2o37R_AJw5opPQ","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"299","text":"Evitar restricciones físicas → empeoran inmovilidad","guid":"jCsqfongd6Ce5W_RKJH4sQ","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"299","text":"Adecuación del nivel de cuidado según CFS","guid":"0GKiTQpl1rvGAWGfzsuzfw","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"299","text":"LPP Kennedy terminal → pera, mariposa, sacra-coxígea","guid":"kd4k_z-eCsgE-YPkkX06uA","children":[{"id":"304","parent":"303","text":"Aparición 24-48h pre-muerte","guid":"86FSrun-RgizJSYS6H5XXg","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"303","text":"Reconocer → objetivos PALIATIVOS, no curativos","guid":"Hdt-uWEGe8XppA142MN1yg","children":[]}]},{"id":"306","parent":"299","text":"Proporcionalidad terapéutica en paciente frágil avanzado","guid":"1cK9SgvvGs0vOCGlkWN95g","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"299","text":"LPP marcador de TRANSICIÓN → activar paliativismo si etapa 3-4 + fragilidad terminal","guid":"neWfdXVruXUjIDcMEygR-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"308","parent":"0","text":"Cuidados Paliativos en LPP (WHS 2023)","guid":"ceoYAe_xcsEKWdieCcQ7vQ","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"Objetivos → CONFORT, control síntomas, dignidad","guid":"Py7WQMXEx9Le4PTFHFptCA","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"308","text":"No siempre es realista cicatrizar","guid":"V8tQBPiflIkPuVNVvW5UUw","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"308","text":"Enfoque SCALE → Skin Changes At Life's End","guid":"D4xy8YHQfAqe6WOWqY4H_Q","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"308","text":"Manejo síntomas","guid":"VC57GNqxLmw16F5xalxR-w","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"Dolor → opioides sistémicos + tópicos","guid":"IIMKZBSgx9q03FYcPctamQ","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"312","text":"Olor → carbón activado, metronidazol tópico","guid":"cE3dZ4XBLb7w6EDfHdrCfg","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"312","text":"Exudado → superabsorbentes","guid":"Cyl6IIV4D2NdvZ4GGMtPRg","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"312","text":"Sangrado → alginatos, adrenalina tópica","guid":"5XZEuS29c8oL6NU6bWmFZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"317","parent":"308","text":"Frecuencia de curación → menor (evitar trauma)","guid":"QsEb5pQ81d32BcVQbMDlog","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"308","text":"Comunicación con familia → realismo pronóstico","guid":"qYTMcwWyagAVi0VQNZrK5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"319","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"OYnCyRboCm7nzy8zr72ofA","children":[{"id":"320","parent":"319","text":"Braden <=12 → activar bundle prevención INMEDIATO (superficie + cambios posición + nutrición)","guid":"uDCpUym9ouxevNu9aFgYXQ","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"319","text":"LPP = evento adverso TRAZADOR de calidad → auditar siempre","guid":"st5wWWS0gRs8gN3MyW5ymQ","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"319","text":"DTPI puede evolucionar a etapa 3-4 en 48-72h → monitoreo estrecho","guid":"fwCbiTHIF9_J96brRzhfoQ","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"319","text":"NO DESBRIDAR talón con escara seca estable sin signos inflamación (AGS Choosing Wisely)","guid":"FsNRcDByaGHVSqE6lUetyg","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"319","text":"Apósito espuma silicona PROFILÁCTICO en sacro/talones reduce HAPI en UCI → implementar al ingreso si Braden <=14","guid":"jn8nBZDfjoNZUddT2adEyw","children":[]},{"id":"325","parent":"319","text":"Mascarilla VMNI → hidrocoloide fino o espuma silicona en puente nasal desde inicio","guid":"CVU6D-3t2w16VVdGyOUUzw","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"319","text":"Revisar cabecera <=30° → previene cizallamiento sacro","guid":"4fPfhiqUN0h-q47GTIV2_w","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"319","text":"Albúmina <3.5 + CFS >=5 + Braden <=12 → TRIADA de ALTO RIESGO → superficie dinámica","guid":"_CM6LOZOrb6AkfFYKGKaEw","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"319","text":"LPP etapa 3-4 en AM frágil con comorbilidad avanzada → considerar CFS y objetivos de cuidado antes que cirugía agresiva","guid":"S450qXTklCHTeZx7vowe-Q","children":[]},{"id":"329","parent":"319","text":"Plata tópica >14 días sin evolución → reevaluar (biofilm, osteomielitis, isquemia)","guid":"z2bt2P2LXztmRAcWY6_G7g","children":[]},{"id":"330","parent":"319","text":"Osteomielitis sospechada → probe-to-bone, RM, biopsia ósea → NO antibióticos empíricos prolongados","guid":"6ftzazAeqGHQ-r9Z8iQC1w","children":[]},{"id":"331","parent":"319","text":"LPP Kennedy = signo de agonía, NO falla de cuidado → comunicar a familia","guid":"lmBb0p_NeHxtGN_VwfYI-A","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"319","text":"Hidrocoloide NUNCA en lesión infectada ni en etapa 3-4 profunda","guid":"fjV4EQ6_z1R6apZ25gGuzQ","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"319","text":"Heridas secas necróticas → hidrogel + apósito oclusivo (autolítico)","guid":"8_XX7Gp5lYrD3K89xNBr8w","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"319","text":"Heridas muy exudativas → hidrofibra o superabsorbente > alginato","guid":"sJYrUFuPveRBnGQIM7rBVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"335","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"2SuGFYYLUv3z33plltlNwg","children":[{"id":"336","parent":"335","text":"1. European Pressure Ulcer Advisory Panel, National Pressure Injury Advisory Panel, Pan Pacific Pressure Injury Alliance. Prevention and Treatment of Pressure Ulcers/Injuries: Clinical Practice Guideline. 3rd ed. EPUAP/NPIAP/PPPIA; 2019.","guid":"0Xj22fKa4kqYP_72WTiwxQ","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"335","text":"2. Gould LJ, Alderden J, Aslam R, et al. WHS guidelines for the treatment of pressure ulcers-2023 update. Wound Repair Regen. 2023;32(1):6-33. doi:10.1111/wrr.13130","guid":"V4Zw-lLYBdqomNs7DVxn7g","children":[]},{"id":"338","parent":"335","text":"3. Cowan L, Broderick V, Alderden JG. Pressure Injury Prevention Considerations for Older Adults. Crit Care Nurs Clin North Am. 2020;32(4):601-609. doi:10.1016/j.cnc.2020.08.009","guid":"8fh80x4E8ndZCVWlSL5n1g","children":[]},{"id":"339","parent":"335","text":"4. Sillmon K, Moran C, Shook L, Lawson C, Burfield AH. The Use of Prophylactic Foam Dressings for Prevention of Hospital-Acquired Pressure Injuries: A Systematic Review. J Wound Ostomy Continence Nurs. 2021;48(3):211-218. doi:10.1097/WON.0000000000000762","guid":"oC-G1SmZ1RXjvb7m4LiSIw","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"335","text":"5. Lyu Y, Huang YL, Li ZY, Lin F. Interventions and strategies to prevent medical device-related pressure injury in adult patients: A systematic review. J Clin Nurs. 2023;32(19-20):6863-6878. doi:10.1111/jocn.16790","guid":"iaaLc2iNlwLI6Yzeuz8MNQ","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"335","text":"6. Emami Zeydi A, Zare-Kaseb A, Nazari AM, et al. Mask-related pressure injury prevention associated with non-invasive ventilation: A systematic review. Int Wound J. 2024;21(6):e14909. doi:10.1111/iwj.14909","guid":"m_utii29CkJQ3xtJluAUzQ","children":[]},{"id":"342","parent":"335","text":"7. Tzen YT, Sambandam S, Delmore B, et al. Clinical Risk Factors of Perioperative Pressure Injury in Older Adult Patients with a Hip Fracture. Adv Skin Wound Care. 2023;36(12):642-650. doi:10.1097/ASW.0000000000000068","guid":"2G-XEs-Kx1ByujazaylkQg","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"335","text":"8. Ministerio de Salud de Chile. Norma General N°0006: Prevención de Úlceras por Presión. Santiago: MINSAL; 2018.","guid":"SnMpwg5-hUSsxI9ZeOXXIQ","children":[]},{"id":"344","parent":"335","text":"9. Ministerio de Salud de Chile. Orientación Técnica sobre Prevención de Lesiones por Presión. Santiago: MINSAL; 2023.","guid":"ewLL14JSckhYIrEXayYyjg","children":[]},{"id":"345","parent":"335","text":"10. Instituto Nacional de Heridas. Guía Clínica Manejo Integral de la Úlcera por Presión. Santiago: INHERIDAS; 2016.","guid":"pygXPNjhl6lZdEdxU3FEow","children":[]},{"id":"346","parent":"335","text":"11. Edsberg LE, Black JM, Goldberg M, et al. Revised NPUAP Pressure Injury Staging System. J Wound Ostomy Continence Nurs. 2016;43(6):585-597.","guid":"3kHwSQletu4O9eCLbCujjg","children":[]},{"id":"347","parent":"335","text":"12. Munro N. Pressure Injury Staging Update 2019: A New Pressure Injury Stage. Crit Care Nurs Clin North Am. 2020;32(4):537-546.","guid":"4F-KMfxZSMX_qijHirl8hw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":347,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Imported","filename":"LPP curaciones avanzadas Chile","id":"map_2494","resolved_references":[]}